{"tid":563240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]反鏝反哥麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-02-16T16:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T18:30:38.000Z","uid":108862,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c2e945a6947505ddab9ca80c88354ed4a21c48","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 見到反鏝反哥又出現(<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/562991/page/2?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/562991/page/2?ref=ios</a>)，諗起之前睇過嘅一大段英文長文。唔想睇我鳩譯嘅可以自己睇: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/larriepeniel/status/942393173363576832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flarriepeniel%2Fstatus%2F942393173363576832&d=NuC2pLmyAj%2BpAB0WRKJ8HsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=67f4a496\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flarriepeniel%2Fstatus%2F942393173363576832&h=d8a48735\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/larriepeniel/status/942393173363576832</a><br />\n<br />\n利申疤</span>"},{"pid":"3faaea736dc01f5bf99c582e35a6ca442f816144","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"杜格利殊於1991年10月出任布力般流浪的領隊，首年即能帶領球隊回升新成立的英超。布力般流浪的新班主是極具野心的大有錢人，於是金錢足球遊戲揭開序幕。<br />\n<br />\n1992年，布力般流浪搶贏曼聯，以破英格蘭記錄的<span style=\"color: red;\">3.6m</span>(鎊，下同)羅致舒利亞。<br />\n<br />\n1993年，以<span style=\"color: red;\">2.4m</span>買入Tim Flowers，創下英國最貴門將記錄。<br />\n<br />\n1994年，再以破紀錄的<span style=\"color: red;\"> 5m</span>從諾域治買下Chris Sutton(唔識佢)，組成英格蘭歷史上最貴的鋒線組合<span style=\"color: red;\">(8.6m)</span>。<br />\n<br />\n加上同期買入的Henning Berg, Ian Pearce, Graeme Le Saux, Stuart Ripley, Mark Atkins, Tim Sherwood, and Jason Wilcox，升班不久的布力般流浪於1994年球季排名第二，並於1995年贏下英超冠軍。先後打破轉會費紀錄的兩人，該季分別攻入34、15球。用錢買冠軍的球隊，早在1995年就出現了。"},{"pid":"b5c1855daddd3aa8b5543722d59a3b7b269b9495","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:57:52.000Z","msg":"於是曼聯出手了。<br />\n<br />\n94/95球季，費爵爺以<span style=\"color: red;\">7m</span>買入安迪高爾(Andy Cole)，<span style=\"color: red;\">1.25m</span>買入David May。<br />\n<br />\n95/96球季，<span style=\"color: red;\">1.3m</span>買Jordi Cryuff，<span style=\"color: red;\">3.5m</span>買普波斯基，<span style=\"color: red;\">1.5m</span>買Ole Solskjaer，<span style=\"color: red;\">1.2m</span>買Ronny Johnsen。<br />\n<br />\n96/97球季，<span style=\"color: red;\">1.5m</span>買Eric Nevland，<span style=\"color: red;\">3.5m</span>Teddy Sheringham。<br />\n<br />\n97/98球季，<span style=\"color: red;\">1.15m</span>買Jonathan Greening，<span style=\"color: red;\">5m</span>買Henning Berg。<br />\n<br />\n98/99球季，<span style=\"color: red;\">12.6m</span>買Dwight Yorke ，<span style=\"color: red;\">4.4m</span>買Jesper Blomqvist，<span style=\"color: red;\">10.75m</span>買史譚。<br />\n<br />\n有費爵爺大洗特洗，布力般流浪贏後的6年，曼聯5奪英超，98/99球季三冠王。<br />\n<br />\n不過有人說過費爵爺買冠軍嗎？沒有。"},{"pid":"09c0d3a2679fabbb4d0412a1cf8102db6df52fa7","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"01/02年球季，費sir以<span style=\"color: red;\">19m</span>簽下雲尼史達萊，又以破英超記錄的<span style=\"color: red;\">28.1m</span>簽下華朗。翌年再破紀錄，以<span style=\"color: red;\">29.1m</span>簽下里奧費迪南。<br />\n<br />\n但有人說費爵爺金錢足球嗎？沒有。"},{"pid":"5e16b7e6e056fae63958583cea32b6917701b9ac","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"直到油王先後入主車路士、曼城，忽然就有人抱怨金錢足球了。"},{"pid":"d28403d4ca3262f3d7d39c8d5e344ff5142601bd","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"但洗錢就一定贏得到冠軍了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n13/14年球季，熱刺花了<span style=\"color: red;\">103.7m</span>，聯賽卻僅排第六；排名第二、第四的利物普和阿仙奴僅花費<span style=\"color: red;\">42.5m</span>及<span style=\"color: red;\">48m</span>。<br />\n<br />\n14/15球季，曼聯用了<span style=\"color: red;\">145.5m</span>後排第四，仍不及只花<span style=\"color: red;\">87.5m</span>後排第二的曼城。<br />\n<br />\n15/16球季，阿仙奴僅花<span style=\"color: red;\">15m</span>排名第二；曼城用<span style=\"color: red;\">152.1m</span>後排第四，曼聯用<span style=\"color: red;\">103.6m</span>後排第五。"},{"pid":"9906b989308b9808616e94d8aacf7c03fb8384f4","tid":563240,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"過多兩年都無獌再敢笑金錢足球啦<br />\n仲講黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6060b05604029789fe164224f7c9edfa9b9e6a30","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"16/17球季，哥迪奧拿正式入主曼城。由那刻起，英超最大洗的三隊如下:<br />\n<br />\n曼城: <span style=\"color: red;\">168m</span> (16/17) &amp; <span style=\"color: red;\">212m</span> (17/18)<br />\n車路士: <span style=\"color: red;\">119m</span> (16/17) &amp; <span style=\"color: red;\">187m</span> (17/18)<br />\n曼聯: <span style=\"color: red;\">149m</span> (16/17) &amp; <span style=\"color: red;\">146m</span> (17/18)<br />\n<br />\n玩金錢足球的，又豈止曼城一隊。如果有邊隊有資格出聲，肯定唔係上面嗰兩隊先。"},{"pid":"19a0f4b11f89d00a185865112d2a298e0d641923","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"同場加映: 哥狗大清瘀血<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/010948_1ca398a73215e004bbc49e549616802c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F010948_1ca398a73215e004bbc49e549616802c.png&h=85d1d2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/010948_68a7066f938c472f605a9c41514820e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F010948_68a7066f938c472f605a9c41514820e1.png&h=c3b9253f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f7a24ab67cee66ef970c783f75e2087e5a6a0a6","tid":563240,"uid":760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"啲死曼狗係咁，樓豬唔好嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7522706f7dc3c7bbc365242f4be4255f0667aa","tid":563240,"uid":5549,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"費狗咪又係買金錢足球，買里奧費迪南貴撚到"},{"pid":"9ffc4b9c56ed386563423ecf1975ef41c1910b84","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f7a24ab67cee66ef970c783f75e2087e5a6a0a6","tid":563240,"uid":760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"啲死曼狗係咁，樓豬唔好嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"純粹想睇吓曼聯迷有咩回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2964e23657e537006f9f4d678053ae79ff3f9ec4","tid":563240,"uid":27416,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"聽曼迷講佢地係白手興家<br />\n你地係石油足球"},{"pid":"fe5695b0c7e3ea900400e3188887066969059bee","tid":563240,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3dd2af31ae2a8bb8b132f512a32511272ca537","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799ec4ea6a0abf1fe38d0feddba47872337580a9","tid":563240,"uid":104268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc21b685c858d1f6e0eefd641d0d0d5a90e6ccfe","tid":563240,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6060b05604029789fe164224f7c9edfa9b9e6a30","tid":563240,"uid":108862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"16/17球季，哥迪奧拿正式入主曼城。由那刻起，英超最大洗的三隊如下:<br />\n<br />\n曼城: <span style=\"color: red;\">168m</span> (16/17) &amp; <span style=\